  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1940490/extras/2d66a33d01064d362e473d37c366ba72.avif?t=1727386791\" width=596 height=202 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1940490/extras/c3a9d73db99c272a0176a5fce7a77ffa.avif?t=1727386791\" width=596 height=306 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destroy the blocks you achieve a 80% score while avoiding enemies and their attacks. Improve your time and unlock additional levels!.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1940490/extras/bdc017f45e0d19b96cd4119f12318bb7.avif?t=1727386791\" width=596 height=306 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 unique levels and 5 bosses with different techniques to challenge you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1940490/extras/56a1668bdda5c53c9e225c26e9bf78f0.avif?t=1727386791\" width=596 height=306 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi, I'm Nicolas Rizzi, just a guy who loves making games. 'TileBreaker' was my first creation; it's a bit rough around the edges, but filled with passion and fun gameplay. I poured a lot of love into it, learning and growing along the way. I truly hope you enjoy playing it as much as I enjoyed creating it. If you do, feel free to check out my other works. Here's to more gaming adventures together!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1940490/extras/738e592c2ca15d8d0eab3862e7a60356.avif?t=1727386791\" width=596 height=306 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1940490/extras/2d66a33d01064d362e473d37c366ba72.avif?t=1727386791\" width=596 height=202 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1940490/extras/c3a9d73db99c272a0176a5fce7a77ffa.avif?t=1727386791\" width=596 height=306 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destroy the blocks you achieve a 80% score while avoiding enemies and their attacks. Improve your time and unlock additional levels!.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1940490/extras/bdc017f45e0d19b96cd4119f12318bb7.avif?t=1727386791\" width=596 height=306 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 unique levels and 5 bosses with different techniques to challenge you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1940490/extras/56a1668bdda5c53c9e225c26e9bf78f0.avif?t=1727386791\" width=596 height=306 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi, I'm Nicolas Rizzi, just a guy who loves making games. 'TileBreaker' was my first creation; it's a bit rough around the edges, but filled with passion and fun gameplay. I poured a lot of love into it, learning and growing along the way. I truly hope you enjoy playing it as much as I enjoyed creating it. If you do, feel free to check out my other works. Here's to more gaming adventures together!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1940490/extras/738e592c2ca15d8d0eab3862e7a60356.avif?t=1727386791\" width=596 height=306 /></span></p>",
